Lux LSP is part of the Lux language project. It is designed to provide language
server support, VS Code integration, and Garry's Mod API intelligence for Lux.

Garry's Mod API documentation data must be sourced from official/public
documentation with attribution. GLua Enhanced is treated as a user-experience
reference only; Lux LSP must not copy its GPL implementation or bundled data.
